CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1967, pg. 12, reads: "Durett [Durrett] Goes Up - Going up for a goal is Kenneth Durett [Durrett], center of the victorious Schenley High School Spartans, as Paul Leonard (14) and Paul Litz look on.  The Spartans triumphed with relative ease."
TitMainTitle: Schenley High School basketball player Kenneth "Kenny" Durrett shooting basket in city championship game against South Hills, Civic Arena
